headline: RTX to release third quarter earnings results on October 21, 2025
summary: RTX (NYSE: RTX) will issue its third quarter 2025 earnings results on Tuesday, October 21, prior to the stock market opening. A conference call will take place at 8:30 a.m. ET to discuss the results.
